Package: speedfetch
Version: 1.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: MyNameIsV <allstalkermak@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/MyNamesV/speedfetch
Description: Fast Linux system information fetcher
 SpeedFetch is a minimalist and fast C++ utility for displaying
 Linux system information with beautiful ASCII art of the distribution.
 Supports multiple Linux distributions with colored terminal output.
